---
import { siteConfig } from "../../site.config";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-28 px-4">
  <!-- Subtle grid background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(#1D3557 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to right, #1D3557 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative">
    <!-- Badge urgence -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-8 fade-up">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full pulse-signal"></span>
      47% des actifs français envisagent une reconversion (Ipsos 2026)
    </div>

    <h1 class="mb-6 fade-up" data-speakable>
      Le monde du travail change.
      <br />
      <span style={`color: ${siteConfig.colors.primary};`}>Toi aussi, tu dois changer.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 fade-up" data-speakable>
      L'IA transforme chaque métier. Certains disparaissent, d'autres se reinventent, de nouveaux emergent. Adapte-toi t'aide à comprendre ce qui se passe, et surtout a agir.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center fade-up">
      <a
        href="/metiers"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg"
        style={`background: ${siteConfig.colors.primary};`}
      >
        Mon métier est-il menace ?
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/guides"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-gray-700 font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-primary/30 hover:text-primary transition-all"
      >
        Guides de reconversion
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust indicators -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 mt-12 text-sm text-gray-400 fade-up">
      <span>Sources : OCDE, McKinsey, Anthropic, FMI</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>100% indépendant</span>
      <span>·</span>
      <span>Zero formation à vendre</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
